restlib

Class ContentInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • restlib.ContentInfo
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContentInfoWrapper

    @Immutable
public abstract class ContentInfo
extends Object
    Content properties of an HTTP message entity. Client preferences that may be used by a server to perform content negotiation. Implementations must be immutable or effectively immutable.
